  "texts": [
    "However, we find that such type of memory is rarely documented in the literature.",
    "Our speculation is that the agents are always situated in continuous and dynamic environments, with consecutive actions displaying a high correlation.",
    "Therefore, the capture of short-term memory is very important and usually cannot be disregarded.Memory formats: In addition to the memory structure, another perspective to analyze the memory module is based on the formats of the memory storage medium, for example, natural language memory or embedding memory.",
    "Different memory formats possess distinct strengths and are suitable for various applications.",
    "In the following, we introduce several representative memory formats.• Natural languages."
  ]
